  "short_description": "game is developed using Javafx. This is a 2D side-scrolling game. There are three professions in the game. The game is divided into 8 levels with gradually increasing difficulty, and the total game time is 20 hours. The game map is full scene, with a bright pixel art style high frame rate display",
