  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are no language restrictions, and the menu is very simple</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Introduction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are over 20 types of monsters in the game, and 3 bosses will summon small monsters when half blooded. If the BOSS can be activated in seconds, it will not trigger summoning. 3 character roles and 8 levels. When clearing all monsters in the current level, it will prompt to enter the next level.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill Description</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During a successful attack, the monster will appear invincible, and in this case, it is impossible to defeat the monster. The invincible state will only disappear after the monster launches a single strike. All characters and monsters will have a time control in the event of injury, and no actions can be taken under this time control.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Knight Class: High Merit and High Defense</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mage profession: high skill, low defense</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thief profession: Low power High speed</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras/745d9ae063b32c98a7e478726724dd3a.avif?t=1738032654\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras_big/745d9ae063b32c98a7e478726724dd3a.avif?t=1738032654 width=800 height=436 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Eight levels</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full scene levels built in 2D landscape mode. The last two levels are particularly difficult, as the monster's movement speed and attack speed are very fast.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras/27981c013feb727e0d835826b379efd1.avif?t=1738032654\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras_big/27981c013feb727e0d835826b379efd1.avif?t=1738032654 width=800 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras/e8e566ea15f4f430823fc004c420f8fc.avif?t=1738032654\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras_big/e8e566ea15f4f430823fc004c420f8fc.avif?t=1738032654 width=800 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras/82210671b2b8baec4cff812fddb4b22c.avif?t=1738032654\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras_big/82210671b2b8baec4cff812fddb4b22c.avif?t=1738032654 width=800 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras/9e9e4349b261510a184e87485c46d1f9.avif?t=1738032654\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras_big/9e9e4349b261510a184e87485c46d1f9.avif?t=1738032654 width=800 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras/a53ce7b10d5a48b44ffbf33e867be541.avif?t=1738032654\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras_big/a53ce7b10d5a48b44ffbf33e867be541.avif?t=1738032654 width=800 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras/7be09918836fc48a33b416aad450a6da.avif?t=1738032654\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras_big/7be09918836fc48a33b416aad450a6da.avif?t=1738032654 width=800 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras/66eb7109d92075ef245b2f3ffdbaec82.avif?t=1738032654\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras_big/66eb7109d92075ef245b2f3ffdbaec82.avif?t=1738032654 width=800 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras/4c7d70cdebeba4d9d66500ae44d396fc.avif?t=1738032654\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436980/extras_big/4c7d70cdebeba4d9d66500ae44d396fc.avif?t=1738032654 width=800 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
